# oneforty Seller Demo

This is a Sinatra app that simulates the seller-side logic of a sale that takes place on oneforty.com. 
For more inforation, see http://sandbox.oneforty.com

Install requirements: 

> gem install json
> gem install sinatra

Run like:

> ruby oneforty-seller-demo.rb

Confirm it is running by visiting http://localhost:4567/

It should give a hello world message. If not, logs are in log/sinatra.log.

If you have questions about how to incorporate this logic into your web site, please contact us at developers@oneforty.com.